## **1. Grant of Rights**

Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a copy of this software and associated documentation files (the "Software") to:

- use  
- copy  
- modify  
- merge  
- publish  

**Restrictions:**

You may **not**:

- Rebrand, rename, or change the identity, name, logo, or trademark of this project.  
- Claim this Software as your own work.  
- Remove or modify copyright notices.  
- Repackage, resell, sublicense, or place this project behind a paywall.  
- Sell or monetize the core engine, editor, platform, or code.  
- Integrate paid or restricted features directly into the core engine.  

You **may**:

- Build software **on top of this project**.  
- Develop commercial tools, services, and applications using this engine.  
- Create **paid plugins, extensions, or add-ons**, as long as the core engine remains free, open, and accessible.

---

## **2. Permitted Use**

The Software may be freely used for:

- Personal and hobby projects  
- Learning and education  
- Research  
- Indie and commercial games  
- Music tools, plugins, and services  

---

## **3. Honor-Based Commercial Support**

If you or your company generate **more than USD 100,000 per year** in gross revenue using this Software or derivatives of it, you are **legally required** to:

- Contact the author  
- Provide a **yearly sponsorship of your choice**  

> There is no fixed price. This system is based on **honor, fairness, and mutual respect**, and is intended to support the **development, maintenance, and open community** around the project.

---

## **4. Open-Source & Free Commitment**

- **This project will always remain free and open-source.**  
- The **Music Engine, Editor, Code, Platform, and Brand** will **never be sold, closed, or restricted**.  
- Our obligation is to ensure that **all users always have access** to the full engine.  
- Any attempt to violate this commitment will be considered a license breach and **will be legally pursued**.

---

## **5. Branding, Plugin & Monetization Policy**

- All commercial monetization related to this engine must be implemented as **plugins, extensions, or external services**.  
- Monetizing the core engine, its editor, code, or platform directly is strictly prohibited.  
- Any paid feature must clearly state that it is **not part of the official core distribution**.  

---

## **6. Enforcement**

Any violation of this license, including unauthorized rebranding, monetization, or redistribution, will be actively investigated and legally pursued.

---

## **7. Community Integrity & Abuse**

Abusive, harmful, or fraudulent behavior may result in permanent exclusion from all official project spaces.  

> This does **not** affect legal usage rights.

---

## **8. Open Development**

You are free to:

- fork  
- extend  
- build  

as long as this license remains included and respected.  

> Remixing or renaming the engine itself is **not allowed**; only plugins or external add-ons may be monetized or extended.

---

